<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In general I am pretty sympathetic to the vent=
ure capitalists who invested in FTX. I <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombe=
rgbusiness.com/click/29776711.281548/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcG=
