<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Oh <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusin=
ess.com/click/29776711.281548/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9wcm9maWxlL=
